==Romanian==
===Etymology===
A substratum word like Albanian ''[[buzë]]''. Perhaps both come from a [[PIE]] ''[[*beu-]]''/''[[*bheu-]]'', "to swell" and there is another cognate, Old Irish ''[[bus]]''.
